<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>Placing a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-debugoverlay.xml">DebugOverlay</db:link> in one branch of a custom framegraph will cause an overlay with scene details to be rendered along with the scene.</db:para>
<db:para>The standard <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-extras-forwardrenderer.xml">ForwardRenderer</db:link> includes a <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-render-debugoverlay.xml">DebugOverlay</db:link> node that can be enabled via the <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-extras-forwardrenderer.xml#showDebugOverlay-prop">ForwardRenderer::showDebugOverlay</db:link> property.</db:para>
</db:section>
